  "3099790": {
    "name": "Operation Night Strikers",
    "steam_appid": 3099790,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099790/extras/30d0fbe618d51c9edd9fcbc638fb162f.poster.avif?t=1759138660\" width=600 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099790/extras/30d0fbe618d51c9edd9fcbc638fb162f.webm?t=1759138660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099790/extras/30d0fbe618d51c9edd9fcbc638fb162f.mp4?t=1759138660\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1980年代后半，TAITO所推出的大型街机射击游戏4部名作皆收录于此！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >横扫各种场景，夜晚街道、太空船——不分时间与地点，尽享纵深卷轴射击动作游戏的飨宴！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■<strong>射击游戏名門“TAITO”的代表作大集合！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099790/extras/12b0c8d00dfdf8fd6ad24689870757a5.poster.avif?t=1759138660\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099790/extras/12b0c8d00dfdf8fd6ad24689870757a5.webm?t=1759138660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099790/extras/12b0c8d00dfdf8fd6ad24689870757a5.mp4?t=1759138660\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>收录作品一览</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >OPERATION WOLF<br>OPERATION THOUNDERBOLT<br>NIGHT STRIKER<br>SPACE GUN</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>OPERATION WOLF</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手持连发机枪与火箭筒，单枪匹马潜入敌军基地，营救被囚禁于收容所的人质并带他们逃出生天吧！作战代号“狼作战（OPERATION WOLF）”的任务绝不容许失败！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>OPERATION THOUNDERBOLT</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了拯救遭到恐怖份子劫机绑架的人质，《OPERATION WOLF》的主角“Roy Adams”与他的旧战友“Hardy Jones”再度集结，展开全新的人质救援任务“OPERATION THOUNDERBOLT”！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>NIGHT STRIKER</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为联合国特务机关所属的特别行动部队，人称“NIGHT STRIKER”，驾驶高速战斗悬浮机“INTER-GRAY”，贯穿霓虹闪烁的未来都市，歼灭邪恶的恐怖组织！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SPACE GUN</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2039年的宇宙开发时代。调查不明事故的宇宙海军突袭队员，潜入一艘发出求救讯号的宇宙货船内部，所目睹的景象是……！？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操控高性能连发枪械，潜入太空船的未知恐怖中救出人质吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■更加舒适的游玩体验！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099790/extras/0dff14de7e18ccb948945dd6c3c370e0.poster.avif?t=1759138660\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099790/extras/0dff14de7e18ccb948945dd6c3c370e0.webm?t=1759138660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099790/extras/0dff14de7e18ccb948945dd6c3c370e0.mp4?t=1759138660\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>辅助配件功能</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用所有收录作品的专属辅助配件进行游戏吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>OPERATION WOLF</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・HP情报<br>・武器情报<br>・关卡情报<br>・命中率（Hit Rate）<br>・等级＆游戏版本<br>・背景音乐情报</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>OPERATION THOUNDERBOLT</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・HP情报<br>・武器情报<br>・命中率（Hit Rate）<br>・等级＆游戏版本<br>・背景音乐情报<br>・任务情报</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>NIGHT STRIKER</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・分歧情报<br>・奖励纪录<br>・行进奖励<br>・等级＆游戏版本<br>・魔王情报<br>・反战＆清空奖励<br>・输入情报<br>・背景音乐情报</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SPACE GUN</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・等级＆游戏版本<br>・HP情报<br>・枪械情报<br>・武器情报<br>・魔王情报<br>・背景音乐情报</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >透过专属辅助配件，享受全面升级的游玩乐趣！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在“OPERATION WOLF”与“OPERATION THOUNDERBOLT”中，透过“HP资讯”与“武器资讯”辅助配件，能轻鬆掌握剩馀HP与弹药数量，并透过“命中率（Hit Rate）”辅助配件确认击倒敌人数与玩家的命中率。成为不畏敌军总攻击的强悍军人，以及一发必中名不虚传的神射手，成功完成任务吧！<br><br>在“NIGHT STRIKER”中，透过“分歧资讯”、“奖励纪录”以及“行进奖励”辅助配件，可以轻鬆掌握目前进入的分歧关卡、游玩过程中获得的奖励纪录，以及战斗悬浮机的行进奖励。穿越多样的分歧地图，挺进拥有魔王坐镇的区域吧！透过“魔王资讯”辅助配件来获取等待著玩家的对手情报并做好准备，就能迈向胜利！<br><br>在宇宙动作射击游戏“SPACE GUN”中，玩家可同时操作多种枪械与武器，透过“武器资讯”与“枪械资讯”辅助配件，能查看目前使用的武器名称与类型，甚至是所持有的弹药数。善用这些辅助配件导出最佳策略，在未知的恐怖之中杀出一条生路！<br><br>此外，所有收录作品皆根据当时推出的机台与版本，提供更加崭新的游戏体验。透过“等级＆游戏版本”辅助配件，可确认目前游玩的游戏版本与当前的游戏等级；而使用“背景音乐资讯”辅助配件，则能进一步了解那些令人怀念的乐曲，轻鬆搜寻并回味昔日的名曲！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>追加便利功能</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入了储存／读取功能，游玩中可以自由地储存进度并读取资料。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还可以在线上传自己的游玩纪录，或下载高排名玩家的视频进行播放。此外，亦可通过变更设定，在游戏画面中套用模拟显像管风格的滤镜，让您享受怀旧的乐趣！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持“Cyber Stick intelligent controller”！<br>各作品也预定收录家用主机移植版！</p>",
